description:
Variation of conditions 8(Controlling Dual Uses), 9(Balance of Uses), 11(Customer Opening Times) 15(Ground Floor Frontages) and 52(BREEAM) of planning permission 15/04500/FUL (Redevelopment of Thrayle House for residential-led mixed use development up to 20 storeys, comprising 177 homes (Class C3), and 1,358 sq m of flexible retail (Class A1 and A2) and community space (Class D1).) granted on 14.09.2016.

Variation sought: Inclusion of B1 use to the ground floor frontage units and amend wording of conditions 8, 9, 11, 15 and 52
